data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Homes with an in-ground backyard pool are rare in this price range in Tampa Bay.  Featuring vaulted ceilings, this home feels much larger and is light and airy.  With no HOA fees nor restrictions this house would be ideal for a rental Investment property (AirBnB may be possible), retirement home, 2nd home or for your first home.   The yard is fully fenced and is a corner lot with an off street parking pad for 4 cars.  The bathrooms have been tastefully updated.  The pool area features a Tiki Hut for fun pool parties.  The assigned public schools are superior and the K-8 Hillsborough Academy of Math and Science Charter School is right down the street.  Alonso High also offers an International Baccalaureate High School Magnet program.  Located within 15 minutes of Tampa Int'l, 20 minutes to The International Mall, Westshore & MidTown and 25 minutes to some of the most beautiful beaches in Tampa Bay.  Walking distance to the Supermarket and the beautiful Upper Tampa Bay Trail to enjoy walks and bike rides in nature is just a half of a mile away.  APPOINTMENT REQUIRED for backup offers--24 hours before, Mon-Sat 10 am to 5 pm only.  No Sunday showings.  Please contact Hillsborough County to verify short term rental requirements.
